  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of the present study is to determine the impact of preoperative IV-iron (ferric
      carboxy maltose) supplementation on postoperative hematocrit values and allogenic blood
      transfusion amount in patients undergoing elective prognathic surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
